+0.150~+0.450 > S 0:0(0) win 65535 <...>
+0.000 < S. 0:0(0) ack 1 win 65535 <mss 1000,sackOK,nop,nop,nop,wscale 0>
+0.000 > . 1:1(0) ack 1 win 65535
+0.010 `$TCP_IP_PD_CASE ctl status`

`$TCP_IP_PD_CASE cleanup`
